description:
Japanese title: Yomigaeru Shishi よみがえる獅子.

In the world of the living, Don Kanonji tries to up the ratings of his television show by recruiting Kon as the mascot of his show.
name: The Reviving Lion

description:
Japanese title: Shokei no Asa 処刑の朝.

Preparations are underway for Rukia's execution...
name: Morning Of The Sentence

description:
Japanese title: Renji, Tamashii no Chikai! Byakuya to no Shitō, 恋次、魂の誓い！白哉との死闘.

While Ichigo continues his Bankai training, Renji emerges from his to try and save Rukia.
name: Renji, Oath Of The Soul! Death Match With Byakuya

description:
Japanese title: Ichimaru Gin no Yūwaku, Kuzusareta Kakugo, 市丸ギンの誘惑、崩された覚悟.

As Rukia Kuchiki is being lead to her execution, she is stopped by the ever-devious Gin Ichimaru. Just when Rukia has prepared herself for death, her concentration is broken by Gin's offer to let her live...
name: Gin Ichimaru's Temptation, Resolution Shattered

description:
Japanese title: Hatasareru Chikai! Rukia Dakkan Naruka! 果たされる誓い！ルキア奪還なるか.

Rukia stands on the Sokyoku at the brink of her execution, not knowing that help is on the way.
name: An Accomplished Oath! Get Back Rukia!
Birds on a Wire/The Scoring Session/The Animaniacs Suite

description:
Japanese title: Saikyō no Shinigami! Kyūkyoku no Shitei Taiketsu 最強の死神！究極の師弟対決.

While Renji hurries to get Rukia out of harm's way, Ichigo stays behind to hold off Byakuya Kuchiki.
name: The Strongest Shinigami! Ultimate Confrontation Between Teacher And Students

description:
Japanese title: Chōsoku no Tatakai! Bu no Megami, Kessu, 超速の戦い！武の女神、決す.

Captain Ukitake and Captain Kyoraku face the punishment meted out by Head Captain Yamamoto's Zanpakuto.
name: Supersonic Battle! Determine the Goddess of Battle

description:
Japanese title: Senbonzakura, Funsai! Ten o Tsuku Zangetsu 千本桜、粉砕！天を衝く斬月.

Fueled by anger and feelings of abandonment and betrayal, Soi Fon persists in her attempt to destroy her former master Yoruichi Shihouin, but her abilities may be hampered by her cocksure attitude.
name: Senbonzakura, Crushed! Zangetsu Thrusts Through The Sky

description:
Japanese title: Kaihō! Kuroki Yaiba, Kiseki no Chikara, 開放！黒き刃、奇跡の力.

The fierce battle between Ichigo and Captain Byakuya rages on. Ichigo taunts Byakuya and demands that he use his Bankai against him...
name: Unseal! The Black Blade, The Miraculous Power

description:
Japanese title: Shitō Ketchaku! Shiroki Hokori to Kuroki Omoi 死闘決着！白き誇りと黒き想い.

Byakuya Kuchiki may have been impressed by the power exerted by Ichigo, the substitute Soul Reaper, but he's not done fighting yet.
name: Conclusion Of The Death Match! White Pride And Black Desire

description:
Japanese title: Zetsubō no Shinjitsu, Furiorosareta Kyōjin 絶望の真実、振り下ろされた凶刃.

Central 46 is the highest judicial body in the Soul Society. After breaking into Central 46, Captain Hitsugaya and Rangiku discover that the forty Sages and six Judges were slaughtered days earlier.
name: Reality Of The Despair, The Assassin's Dagger Is Swung

description:
Japanese title: Aizen, Tatsu! Osorubeki Yabō 藍染、立つ！恐るべき野望.

After defeating Hitsugaya, Captain Aizen heads for the Execution Grounds. Renji is dumbfounded as he finds himself facing Captains Aizen, Ichimaru, and Tossen at Sokyoku hill...
name: Aizen Stands! Horrible Ambitions

description:
Japanese title: Shūketsuseyo! Saikyō no Shinigami Shūdan 集結せよ！最強の死神集団.

Furious after hearing the news of the defection of three captains, Sajin Komamura arrives at the Sokyoku ready to beat the treachery out of Aizen and his lackeys.
name: Gather Together! Group Of The Strongest Shinigami

description:
Japanese title: Rukia no Ketsui, Ichigo no Omoi ルキアの決意、一護の想い.

Peace returns as the Soul Society recuperates from the deep wounds left by the treachery of Captain Aizen and his partners in crime. Captain Komamura and Lieutenant Hisagi visit the graves of fallen comrades...
name: Rukia's Resolution, Ichigo's Feelings

description:
Japanese title: Shingakki, Gense ni Renji ga Yatte Kita!? 新学期、現世に恋次がやって来た!?

Ichigo and his friends have returned from the Soul Society and are finally able to get back to their "normal" lives.
name: New School Term, Renji Has Come to the Material World?!

description:
Japanese title: Shinobi yoru Kyōfu, Nibanme no Giseisha 忍び寄る恐怖、2番目の犠牲者

Ichigo and his friends meet at school and set out to look for Orihime the day after her disappearance.
name: Creeping Terror, the Second Victim

description:
Japanese title: Toppa seyo! Meikyū ni Hisomu Wana 突破せよ！迷宮に潜む罠.

After Chad's kidnapping, Ichigo and the others go to Urahara to explain their predicament.
name: Break Through! The Trap Hidden in the Labyrinth

description:
Japanese title: Shi no Gēmu! Kieru Kurasumeito 死のゲーム！消えるクラスメイト.

Chad and Orihime are rescued, but when Lirin tells them that one of their friends has been replaced by an impostor, they realize that the game is not over.
name: Death Game! The Missing Classmate

description:
Japanese title: Akuma no Shōtai, Akasareta Himitsu 悪魔の正体、明かされた秘密.

Lirin sets in place a giant gate that begins to devour everything in Karakura Town. The only way to have Chad released and save the town is to destroy the gate.
name: True Identity Of The Devil, The Secret Which Is Revealed

description:
Japanese title: Baunto! Tamashii o Karu Mono-tachi バウント！魂を狩る者たち.

New information has come to light regarding an unusual race known as Bounts. Kisuke Urahara explains that Bounts are beings that gain eternal life by absorbing the souls of humans.
name: Baunt! The Soul Hunters

description:
Japanese title: Rukia no Kikan! Daikō Chīmu Fukkatsu ルキアの帰還！代行チーム復活.

Ichigo and Lirin find themselves in a pinch when they are attacked by the Bount Yoshino Soma and her Doll, Goethe.
name: Return of Rukia! The Substitute Team Revival

description:
Japanese title: Gekitotsu no Toki! Kuinshī ni Semaru Ma no Te, 激突の時！クインシーに迫る魔の手.

Ichigo, Rukia, Orihime, Chad, and Uryu surround the Bount Ryo Udagawa, but they find themselves at a slight disadvantage when he releases the immense power of his Doll, Friede.
name: The Moment of Collision! An Evil Hand Draws Near to the Quincy

description: Ezra faces his greatest challenge as part of his growth as a member of the team.
name: Path of the Jedi

has_staff_review.name: Star Wars Rebels Episode 109 - "Path of the Jedi"

description: Ragna is on a one-man rampage against the ruling body, the Novus Orbis Librarium. And a mysterious woman named Rachel directs him to go to the 13th Hierarchical City of Kagutsuchi next.
name: Crimson Rebel

description: Rachel and Hazama watch over Ragna, hoping against hope that their expectations will be betrayed, in spite of the fact that all has gone as it always has.
name: Successor of the Azure

description: Rachel has her showdown with Takemikazuchi, Hazama shows his true colors, and Ragna faces a fight with yet another bounty hunter.
name: The Observing Eye

description: As Ragna recovers from his wounds, Rachel meets with three mysterious beings and Noel runs into an old friend and classmate from the Military Academy.
name: Probabilistic Events

description: Rachel conducts her own mysterious business as usual, porting from place to place. Kokonoe has her own agenda and sends Tager to carry out a mission. And Ragna works towards a full recovery with the help of some friends.
name: The Pair of White Guns

description: Kokonoe's little gambit with Ragna plays out. In the meantime, Jin is still searching for Ragna, but instead, ends up being found by Bang Shishigami, who wants revenge against Jin.
name: False World

description: Tager continues to slowly track Noel. Noel finds Tsubaki, which results in a complicated showdown. And Rachel leads Ragna to where he needs to be and to confront what he already knows.
name: The Wings of Judgement

description: Hazama throws an obstacle in Ragna's way to buy himself some time. This encounter leads Ragna to have an entirely different sort of experience with Lambda.
name: The Mechanical Soul

description: As Makoto works to get Noel to safety, she explains her faith in Kokonoe and her doubts about Hazama. And Tsubaki finally finds Jin again, who is still struggling to deal with his recalcitrant weapon.
name: The Power of Order

description: Makoto and Noel face off against Hazama as he explains to Noel what her true place is in this world.
name: Coccoon of the Godslayer

description: Terumi's designs for Noel come to fruition and he crows about what he has achieved to Ragna, even as Ragna fights a losing battle against him to save Noel.
name: Murakumo Awakens

description: Kokonoe and Rachel believe that Noel's transformation into Mu is irreversible, but Ragna refuses to give up on Noel.
name: Expense for the Future

description:
Japanese title: Mizu no Kōgeki! Tozasareta Byōin kara no Dasshutsu 水の攻撃！閉ざされた病院からの脱出.

Uryu, who is seriously hurt in the Bount attack, is hospitalized at Karakura Hospital. Ichigo and the others, knowing that Quincys are being targeted, decide to protect Uryu in the hospital...
name: Water Attack! Escape from the Shutdown Hospital

description:
Japanese title: Baunto Shūketsu! Ugokidasu Otoko バウント集結！動き出す男.

Ichigo and the others run from the twin Bounts, Ho and Ban, who have attacked them at the hospital...
name: Gathering of Bounts! The Man Who Makes His Move

description:
Japanese title: Eien o Ikiru Ichizoku no Kioku 永遠を生きる一族の記憶.

Uryu was knocked unconscious during Ho and Ban's attack but was saved by Yoshino...
name: Memories Of An Eternally Living Clan

description:
Japanese title: Jūichibantai Gekishin! Yomigaetta Shinigami 十一番隊激震！よみがえった死神.

Uryu is listening to the history of the Bounts at Yoshino's hideout when Koga, a Bount, attacks. Uryu and Yoshino battle Koga's Steel Doll Dalk, but Yoshino's flame Goethe is no match for the steel Dalk...
name: Earth-Shattering Event at 11th Squad! The Shinigami Who Rises Again

description:
Japanese title: Chikara no Gekitotsu! Furīdo VS Zangetsu 力の激突！フリードVS斬月.

Ichigo, Rukia, Lirin, Noba, and Kurodo enter the Bount mansion and for the first time come face to face with Jin Kariya and the other Bounts...
name: Crashing Force! Friido vs. Zangetsu

description:
Japanese title: Kienu Onnen! Kenpachi ga Kitta Shinigami 消えぬ怨念！剣八が斬った死神.

Udagawa, who betrayed Jin Kariya, is brought down by former Squad 11 Soul Reaper Maki Ichinose. Then Ichinose turns his zanpakuto onto Ichigo...
name: Unfading Grudge! The Shinigami whom Kenpachi Killed

description:
Japanese title: Gotei Jūsantai Kyōgaku!! Rekishi ni Uzumoreta Shinjitsu 護廷十三隊驚愕!!歴史に埋もれた真実.

Thanks to Yoruichi's surprise attack, Ichigo and his cohorts barely manage to escape Jin Kariya's mansion. Uryu and Yoshino have sustained serious injuries and are treated at Urahara's Shop...
name: Shocking Revelations For The Gotei 13 divisions!! The Truth Buried In History

description:
Japanese title: Yoshino, Shi o Kaketa Omoi 芳野、死をかけた想い.

Yoshino leaves the Urahara's Shop at the crack of dawn. Yoshino is aware of Jin Kariya's ambition and is determined to stop him at the risk of her life...
name: Yoshino's Decision of Death

description:
Japanese title: Kyōteki no Kyūshū! Chiisana Saishū Bōei Sen!? 強敵の急襲！小さな最終防衛線!?

Yoshino's death brings forth a massive number of new Dolls known as Bitto for Kariya. Day breaks and Urahara casts a barrier around Urahara's Shop so that Ichigo and the others remain undetected by the Bounts...
name: Assault from a Formidable Enemy! A Tiny Final Line of Defense?!

description:
Japanese title: Hitsugaya Ugoku! Osowareta Machi 日番谷動く！襲われた街.

Several days after Yoshino's death, Kariya's new dolls, the Bitto, begin attacking humans and accumulating souls. The Soul Society also has secretly dispatched a force to the World of the Living, but they are ineffective...
name: Hitsugaya Moves! The Attacked City

description:
Japanese title: Ichigo VS Daruku! Shirakigami no Shutsugen 一護VSダルク！白き闇の出現.

Renji's soul disappears after he is attacked by the Bitto. Ichigo, Rukia, Orihime, and Chad desperately search the town for Renji...
name: Ichigo vs. Dalk! Appearance of the Faded Darkness

description:
Japanese title: Haiiro no Kage, Dōru no Himitsu 灰色の影、ドールの秘密.

Rukia and Orihime are having a difficult time fighting Yoshi. They decide that Kurodo and Orihime will act as decoys to give Rukia time to unleash a powerful kido...
name: Grey Shadow, The Secret Of The Dolls

description:
Japanese title: Daikō Chīmu Bunretsu? Uragitta Rukia 代行チーム分裂？裏切ったルキア.

Squad 3 Lieutenant Izuru Kira, sent by the Soul Society, saves Ichigo and takes over the fight with Doll Dalk...
name: Dissension in the Substitute Team? Rukia's Betrayal

description:
Japanese title: Namida no Shitō! Rukia VS Orihime 涙の死闘！ルキアVS織姫.

Rukia is possessed by Ritze and obeys Mabashi's orders to attack Orihime. Orihime tries desperately to use her Shunshunrikka powers, but Mabashi draws out Rukia's Soul Reaper powers...
name: Battle of Tears! Rukia vs. Orihime

description:
Japanese title: Rangiku Mau! Mienai Teki o Kire! 乱菊舞う！見えない敵を斬れ.

Chad, Noba and Ururu confront the Bount Sawatari at a park. Just as the battle is about to begin, the Squad 10 Lieutenant, Rangiku Matsumoto, suddenly appear...
name: Rangiku Dances! Slice the Invisible Enemy!

description:
Japanese title: Byakuya Shōshū！ Ugokidasu Gotei Jūsantai 白哉召集！動き出す護廷十三隊.

After a fierce battle, Noba is defeated by Baura's immense power. Ururu and Chad fight on while trying to protect the injured Noba...
name: Byakuya Is Summoned! The Gotei 13 Start to Move

description:
Japanese title: Fukutaichō Zenmetsu!? Chika Dōkutsu no Wana 副隊長全滅!?地下洞窟の罠.

Rukia, Chad, Orihime, Noba, and Kurodo return to Urahara's Shop. While getting medical treatment, they discuss how the Bounts are fighting with more power than ever...
name: Annihilation of the Lieutenants!? Trap in the Underground Cave

description:
Japanese title: Saisen!? Ishida VS Nemu 再戦!?石田VSネム.

Ichigo, Renji, Rukia, Chad, Orihime, and the others enter the cave of the Bounts. As they cautiously proceed, the eyes of the Doll Gesell suddenly appear...
name: Rematch?! Ishida vs. Nemu

description:
Japanese title: Abarai Renji, Tamashii no Bankai! 阿散井恋次、魂の卍解！

Near the end of Gesell's labyrinth, the Doll Gesell reveals her true form to Ichigo and Renji. Ichigo stands ready with his zangetsu, but Renji steps forward and insists on taking her on solo...
name: Renji Abarai, Bankai of the Soul!

description:
Japanese title: Shinigami to Kuinshī, Yomigaeru Chikara 死神とクインシー、よみがえる力.

When Jin Kariya reveals that the true mission of the Bounts is to destroy the Soul Society, Ichigo is shocked. Bounts are by-products of the Soul Society's soul experiments...
name: Shinigami and Quincy, the Reviving Power

description:
Japanese title: Shinigami Sekai e no Totsunyū, Futatabi 死神世界への突入、再び.

Kariya and other Bounts arrive in the Soul Society and find themselves in a fight with Soul Reapers—Lieutenant Omaeda of Squad 2 and Lieutenant Iba of Squad 7.
name: Invasion of the Shinigami World, Again

description:
Japanese title: Baunto Kyōshū! Gekishin no Gotei Jūsantai バウント強襲！激震の護廷十三隊.

Rukia fights with Yoshi, the Bount, in the Rukon district on her way back to rejoining Squad 13. Since Rukia’s Spirit Energy hasn’t fully returned, she finds herself in a pinch.
name: The Bount Assault! The Gotei 13 of Destructive Earthquake

description:
Japanese title: Hitsugaya no Ketsui! Gekitotsu no Tokisemaru 日番谷の決意！激突の時迫る.

Hitsugaya and the others investigate the Senzaikyu, which was destroyed by Jin Kariya and his group. Meanwhile, Rukia, who was injured in a fight with Yoshi, is transferred and treated in the Kuchiki house.
name: Hitsugaya's Decision! The Clash Approaches

description:
Japanese title: Byakuya Shutsujin! Kaze o Saku Sakura no Mai 白哉出陣！風を裂く桜の舞.

Byakuya and Kariya start fighting in a forest in Kusajishi. Kariya attacks Byakuya, who silently thrusts his sword at Kariya. During the close battle, Byakuya finally releases his zanpakuto, but Kariya’s invisible Dolls bounce the Senbonzakura back.
name: Byakuya Takes the Field! Dance of the Wind-Splitting Cherry Blossoms

description:
Japanese title: Ichigo, Byakuya, Kariya, Sankyoku no Tatakai!" 一護・白哉・狩矢、三極の戦い！

Ichigo rushes to the site where Byakuya and Kariya are fighting and releases his Bankai upon Kariya. Byakuya also releases his Bankai to attack Kariya, but Ichigo and Byakuya are not in sync and can’t harm Kariya.
name: Ichigo, Byakuya, Kariya, The Battle of the Three Extremes!

description:
Japanese title: Hitsugaya Shutsugeki! Mori no Naka no Teki o Kire! 日番谷出撃！森の中の敵を斬れ.

Hitsugaya learns that the Bounts have gathered mobs, so he goes to the forest in Kusajishi with Rangiku and Renji and starts investigating. Meanwhile, buildings in the Seireitei that were destroyed by Ichinose are being restored.
name: Hitsugaya Strikes! Slice the Enemy in the Middle of the Forest

description:
Japanese title: Gekitotsu! Zaraki Kenpachi VS Ichinose Maki 激突！更木剣八VS一之瀬真樹.

Hitsugaya and the others arrive at the Bounts’ hideout, where Ichinose is waiting for them alone. Ichinose plans to detain them himself to help Kariya and his group, who are already headed for the Seireitei.
name: Clash! Zaraki Kenpachi vs. Ichinose Maki

description: A Candy Kingdom slumber party devolves into panic when Finn and Princess Bubblegum vanish.
name: The Pajama War

description: As Agent Carter closes in on Howard Stark's stolen technology, Peggy's secret mission could unravel when the SSR arrests Jarvis and a secret is revealed
name: Time and Tide

description: Robin goes on a quest to gain a new power: whistling.
name: Mouth Hole

description: Snarl and Swoop are added to the Dinobot roster... and just in time!
name: War of the Dinobots

description: Megatron brings Cybertron into Earth orbit to harvest the energy from the destruction caused by Cybertron's gravity.
name: The Ultimate Doom Part 1

description: As Cybertron's orbit ravages Earth, the Autobots take the fight to the Decepticons.
name: The Ultimate Doom Part 3

description: In the aftermath of Cybertron's catastrophic orbit of Earth, both sides regroup, while Starscream puts into motion a plan to destroy the planet.
name: Countdown to Extinction

description: Reports of giant insects terrorizing Bali lead the Decepticons to discover their long-lost comrades, the Insecticons.
name: A Plague of Insects

description: "Megatron challenges Optimus Prime to a one on one battle to end the war."
name: Heavy Metal War

deck: A mutated car goes after Donatello and Casey Jones!
description: When Casey becomes determined to teach a maniac road racer a lesson, he reluctantly turns to Donatello for help.
name: Race With the Demon!

description: When Casey, Raph, Mikey and Donnie are captured by a new mutant, both April and Leo must overcome disabilities in order to save them.
name: Eyes of the Chimera

has_staff_review.name: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Episode 307 - "Eyes of the Chimera"

name: The Riddle in the Middle of the Earth
